var notifs = [];
var added = 0;
siteNotificationKeys = [];
function checkSiteNotifications() {
if (typeof (iziToast) === undefined) {
return;
}
fetch('//notifications.thetrackernetwork.com/api/notifications/?site=Fortnite&userName=124.109.33.50')
.then(function (response) {
return response.json();
})
.then(function (json) {
json.forEach(function (item, index) {
if (siteNotificationKeys.length > 5 || siteNotificationKeys.indexOf(item.RowKey) != -1) {
return;
}
iziToast.show({
title: item.title,
message: item.body,
class: 'trn-izitoast',
closeOnClick: false,
drag: false,
theme: 'dark',
position: 'topRight',
animateInside: false,
layout: 2,
progressBar: false,
timeout: false,
onClosed: function () {
fetch('//notifications.thetrackernetwork.com//api/notifications', {
method: 'DELETE',
headers: {
'Accept': 'application/json',
'Content-Type': 'application/json'
},
body: JSON.stringify({
site: 'Fortnite',
userName: '124.109.33.50',
id: item.RowKey,
type: item.type
})
});
}
});
siteNotificationKeys.push(item.RowKey);
});
});
}
checkSiteNotifications();
setInterval(checkSiteNotifications, 90000);
</script>

<script src="https://trackercdn.com/cdn/fortnitetracker.com/scripts/vue-affix.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/x-template" id="trn-select-template">
<div class="trn-select" :class="{ 'trn-select--disabled': disabled == true, 'trn-select--dot': dot }">
<i v-if="dot" class="trn-select__dot" :style="{ 'background-color': dot }"></i>
<input type="text"
ref="input"
readonly
class="trn-select__input"
:placeholder="placeholder"
v-model="displayText"
v-on:keyup.esc="onEscape"
v-on:keydown.up.prevent="onUp"
v-on:keydown.down.prevent="onDown"
v-on:keydown.enter.prevent="onEnter"
v-on:focus="onFocus"
v-on:blur="onBlur" />
<transition name="trn-select__items" mode="out-in">
<ul class="trn-card trn-select__items trn-card--light" v-if="isOpen">
<li v-for="(item, index) in items"
v-on:mousedown="onSelect(index)"
:class="{ 'trn-select__item': true, 'trn-select__item--active': index == activeIndex, 'trn-select__item--selected': index == selectedIndex }">
{{ item.text }}
</li>
</ul>
</transition>
</div>
</script>
<script type="text/javascript">
Vue.component('trn-select', {
template: '#trn-select-template',
props: {
items: Array,
value: [String, Object, Number],
placeholder: String,
disabled: Boolean,
dot: String
},
data: function () {
return {
isOpen: false,
activeIndex: -1,
internalValue: null,
search: ''
}
},
mounted: function () {
this.internalValue = this.value;
},
computed: {
displayText: function () {
if (this.selectedIndex == -1)
return null;
var item = this.items[this.selectedIndex];
return item.text;
},
selectedIndex: {
get: function () {
return this.getItemIndexByValue(this.internalValue);
},
set: function (newIndex) {
var item = this.items[newIndex];
this.internalValue = item.value;
this.$emit('input', item.value);
}
}
},
watch: {
'value': function (newValue) {
this.internalValue = newValue;
}
},
methods: {
getItemIndexByValue: function (value) {
return this.items.map(function (item) {
return item.value
}).indexOf(value);
},
onSelect: function (index) {
this.selectedIndex = index;
},
onEscape: function () {
this.$refs.input.blur();
},
//onKey: function (e) {
// this.search += String.fromCharCode(e.which).toLowerCase();
// var texts = return this.items.map(function (item) {
// return item.text.toLowerCase()
// });
// console.log(this.search);
//},
onUp: function () {
if (this.activeIndex > 0)
this.activeIndex -= 1;
},
onDown: function () {
if (this.activeIndex < this.items.length - 1)
this.activeIndex += 1;
},
onEnter: function () {
this.selectedIndex = this.activeIndex;
this.$refs.input.blur();
},
onFocus: function () {
this.isOpen = true;
this.activeIndex = this.selectedIndex;
this.search = '';
},
onBlur: function () {
this.isOpen = false;
}
}
})
</script>
<script type="text/x-template" id="trn-picker-template">
<div class="trn-picker">
<div class="trn-picker__container">
<div v-for="(item, index) in items"
v-on:click="onSelect(index)"
:class="{ 'trn-picker__item': true, 'trn-picker__item--active': index == selectedIndex }">{{ item.text }}</div>
</div>
</div>
</script>
<script type="text/javascript">
Vue.component('trn-picker', {
template: '#trn-picker-template',
props: {
items: Array,
value: [String, Object, Number],
},
computed: {
displayText: function () {
if (this.selectedIndex == -1)
return null;
var item = this.items[this.selectedIndex];
return item.text;
},
selectedIndex: {
get: function () {
return this.getItemIndexByValue(this.value);
},
set: function (newIndex) {
var item = this.items[newIndex];
this.$emit('input', item.value);
}
}
},
methods: {
getItemIndexByValue: function (value) {
return this.items.map(function (item) {
return item.value
}).indexOf(value);
},
onSelect: function (index) {
this.selectedIndex = index;
},
}
})
</script>

:data-ad-sticky-container="selectedAd.adStickyContainer"></div>
</template>
</template>
</div>
</script>
<script type="text/javascript">
Vue.component('trn-ad', {
template: '#trn-ad-template',
props: {
name: {
type: String
}
},
mounted: function () {
if (window.timeEnabled === true) {
return
}
this.shouldRender = true
window.addEventListener('resize', this.handleResize)
this.handleResize()
},
beforeDestroy: function () {
window.removeEventListener('resize', this.handleResize)
},
data: function () {
return {
shouldRender: false,
componentWidth: 0,
ads: {
content: [
{
width: 300,
height: 250,
name: 'Fortnite_Desktop_Content_ATF',
alt: '5c87c5e901-296',
showUpsell: true
}
],
sidebar: [
{
width: 300,
height: 600,
name: 'Fortnite_Desktop_Content_300x600',
alt: '5c87c5b977-296',
showUpsell: true
}
]
},
adReport: 'bottom right',
adRefresh: null
}
},
watch: {
'allowRender': function (newValue, oldValue) {
if (newValue !== oldValue && newValue === true) {
this.writeScriptTags()
}
}
},
computed: {
showUpsell: function () {
if (typeof(BT) !== 'undefined' && BT.BLOCKER_ENABLED) {
return false;
} else {
return document.body.classList.contains('show-upsell');
}
},
allowRender: function () {
return this.shouldRender && this.selectedAd != null
},
selectedAd: function () {
var width = this.componentWidth
var adGroup = this.ads[this.name].filter(a => a.width <= width)
if (adGroup.length > 0) {
let ad = adGroup[0]
if (ad.maxContainerSize && width > ad.maxContainerSize) {
return null
}
return ad
}
return null
}
},
methods: {
handleResize: function () {
this.componentWidth = this.$refs.adComponent.clientWidth
},
writeScriptTags: function () {
if (this.$refs.adComponent.querySelector('script') === null) {
//var srcScript = document.createElement('script')
//srcScript.src = '//tags-cdn.deployads.com/a/destinytracker.com.js'
//srcScript.async = true
//if (this.selectedAd.alt) {
// var spanTag = document.createElement('span');
// spanTag.setAttribute('data-uid', this.selectedAd.alt);
// spanTag.setAttribute('style', 'display: none !important');
// spanTag.classList.add('bt-uid-tg');
// this.$refs.adComponent.appendChild(spanTag)
//}
var pushScript = document.createElement('script')
pushScript.innerHTML = '(trnads = window.trnads || []);'
//this.$refs.adComponent.appendChild(srcScript)
this.$refs.adComponent.appendChild(pushScript)
}
}
}
})
</script>
<script>
new Vue({
el: '#app',
data: function () {
return {
event: imp_event,
metadata: imp_metadata,
templates: imp_templates,
leaderboard: imp_leaderboard,
accounts: imp_accounts,
regions: imp_regions,
eventId: 'epicgames_CashCup_Trios1_NAE',
eventWindowId: 'CashCup_Trios1_NAE_Event2',
region: 'NAE',
regionItems: [
{ value: 'NAE', text: 'ðŸŒŽ NA East' },
{ value: 'NAW', text: 'ðŸŒŽ NA West' },
{ value: 'EU', text: 'ðŸŒ Europe' },
{ value: 'OCE', text: 'ðŸŒ Oceania' },
{ value: 'BR', text: 'ðŸŒŽ Brazil' },
{ value: 'ASIA', text: 'ðŸŒ Asia' }
],
isMobile: window && window.matchMedia("(max-width: 998px)").matches,
lbActiveEntryId: null
}
},
mounted: function () {
if (!this.isMobile) {
this.lbActiveEntryId = 0;
}
},
computed: {
eventWindow: function () {
var eventWindowId = this.eventWindowId;
return this.event.event.eventWindows.find(function (window) {
return window.eventWindowId === eventWindowId;
});
},
eventWindowTemplate: function () {
var eventTemplateId = this.eventWindow.eventTemplateId;
return this.templates.find(function (template) {
return template.eventTemplateId === eventTemplateId;
});
},
eventWindowNumber: function () {
var eventWindowId = this.eventWindowId;
return this.event.event.eventWindows.findIndex(function (window) {
return window.eventWindowId == eventWindowId;
}) + 1;
},
regionItemsFiltered: function () {
var regions = this.regions;
return this.regionItems.filter(function (item) {
return regions[item.value] != null;
});
},
templateMaxPoints: function () {
return this.eventWindowTemplate.scoringRules.reduce(function (points, rule) {
points += rule.rewardTiers.reduce(function (points, tier) {
points += tier.pointsEarned;
return points;
}, 0);
return points;
}, 0);
},
lbActiveEntry: function () {
if (this.lbActiveEntryId != null) {
return this.leaderboard.entries[this.lbActiveEntryId]
}
return null
},
lbActiveEntryStats: function () {
var matchesPlayed = this.lbActiveEntry.sessionHistory.length;
return {
pointsEarned: this.lbActiveEntry.pointsEarned,
matchesPlayed: matchesPlayed,
victoryRoyales: this.calculateWins(this.lbActiveEntry.sessionHistory),
kdRatio: this.calculateKd(this.lbActiveEntry.sessionHistory),
avgEliminations: (this.lbActiveEntry.sessionHistory.reduce(function (result, session) {
result += session.trackedStats['TEAM_ELIMS_STAT_INDEX'];
return result;
}, 0) / matchesPlayed).toFixed(2),
avgPlacement: (this.lbActiveEntry.sessionHistory.reduce(function (result, session) {
result += session.trackedStats['PLACEMENT_STAT_INDEX'];
return result;
}, 0) / matchesPlayed).toFixed(2),
avgPTS: (this.lbActiveEntry.pointsEarned / matchesPlayed).toFixed(2)
}
}
},
methods: {
changeRegion: function (region) {
var eventId = this.regions[region];
location.href = '/events/' + eventId;
},
changeEventWindow: function (eventWindowId) {
location.href = '/events/' + this.eventId + '?window=' + eventWindowId
},
changePage: function (page) {
location.href = '/events/' + this.eventId + '?window=' + this.eventWindowId + '&page=' + page
},
formatShortDate: function (date) {
return new Date(date).toLocaleDateString();
},
formatShortTime: function (date) {
return new Date(date).toLocaleTimeString([], {
hour: '2-digit',
minute: '2-digit',
});
},
getDateDiff: function (date, mins) {
var dt = new Date(date);
var newdt = new Date();
newdt.setTime(dt.getTime() + (mins * 60 * 1000));
return this.formatShortTime(newdt);
},
formatDateTime: function (date) {
return new Date(date).toLocaleString();
},
formatNumberWithOrdinal: function (n) {
var s = ["th", "st", "nd", "rd"],
v = n % 100;
return n + (s[(v - 20) % 10] || s[v] || s[0]);
},
formatSeconds: function (sec) {
var minutes = Math.floor(sec / 60);
var seconds = (sec % 60).toString();
if (seconds.length == 1)
seconds = "0" + seconds;
return minutes + ":" + seconds;
},
calculateWins: function (sessionHistory) {
return sessionHistory.reduce(function (result, session) {
result += session.trackedStats['PLACEMENT_STAT_INDEX'] === 1 ? 1 : 0;
return result;
}, 0);
},
calculateKd: function (sessionHistory) {
var kills = sessionHistory.reduce(function (result, session) {
result += session.trackedStats['TEAM_ELIMS_STAT_INDEX'];
return result;
}, 0);
var deaths = sessionHistory.reduce(function (result, session) {
result += session.trackedStats['PLACEMENT_STAT_INDEX'] === 1 ? 0 : 1;
return result;
}, 0);
if (deaths == 0) {
deaths = 1;
}
return (kills / deaths).toFixed(2);
},
averagePlacement: function (sessionHistory) {
var place = sessionHistory.reduce(function (result, session) {
result += session.trackedStats['PLACEMENT_STAT_INDEX'];
return result;
}, 0);
return (place / sessionHistory.length).toFixed(2);
},
getWindowStatus: function (beginTime, endTime) {
beginTime = new Date(beginTime).getTime()
endTime = new Date(endTime).getTime()
var currentTime = new Date().getTime();
if (currentTime > endTime) {
return 'Ended'
}
if (beginTime < currentTime) {
return 'Ongoing';
}
return 'Upcoming';
},
getPlayerName: function (accountId, cleaned) {
var account = this.accounts.find(function (account) {
return account.accountId == accountId;
});
if (account != null) {
if (cleaned) {
return account.playerName;
}
return account.playerName.replace(/[.ã…¤]+$/, '');
} else {
return 'Anonymous'
}
},
getPlayerNameList: function (accountIds) {
var self = this;
return accountIds.map((function (accountId) {
return self.getPlayerName(accountId)
})).join(', ');
},
filterTrackedStats: function (trackedStats) {
delete trackedStats['VICTORY_ROYALE_STAT'];
delete trackedStats['MATCH_PLAYED_STAT'];
return trackedStats;
}
},
directives: {
fitty: {
inserted: function (el) {
fitty(el, {
maxSize: 45
});
}
}
}
});
// Detect if the burbank font has loaded and resize
// the fitty elements so that they fill the space.
if (document.fonts) {
document.fonts.ready.then(function () {
if (document.fonts.check('1em burbank-big')) {
fitty.fitAll();
}
});
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
